              },
              {
                "lang": "en",
                "value": "NAF 2003 and NAF 2008 - Specific nomenclatures for State, regional and Hospital civil service, the MSA, the National Post Office, EDF-GDF Suez, the SNCF for the \"Type of Administrative Structure (STRUC)\" variable and/or the \"Specific profession\" variable (METIE). These nomenclatures can be consulted on the SUMER 2009 collection page on the ministry's website."
